dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jacob Smith. May I have your name, please?
Hi Jacob, my name is Frances Lopez.
Nice to meet you, Frances. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, it's one two three four five.
Great, thank you. And could you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
Thank you, Frances. I have noted the information. Is there anything specific you'd like to inquire about your policy today?
I wanted to check the coverage details for my policy.
Of course, I can assist with that. Let me review your policy details. Thank you for your patience, Frances.
Thank you for your time, Frances. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
